claim.claim-text:
1. A computer implemented pattern correction method, comprising: 
receiving design layout data of a pattern designed by an automated design unit; 
determining an environmental profile based on whether or not another graphics pattern exists at the surrounding in relation to each correction target cell included in said design layout data; 
replacing with a prescribed cell name of correction pattern corresponding to the determined environmental profile by referencing a cell replacement table; and 
importing an OPC correction pattern corresponding to said cell name from a cell library.

11. A pattern correction apparatus, comprising: 
an input/output unit; 
an environmental profile determination unit configured to determine a graphics pattern environment surrounding each correction target cell included in design layout data entered from said input/output unit; 
a cell replacement table configured to store assumable environmental profiles by associating with cell names that are coordinated in one-by-one correspondence with each; 
a cell library configured to associate and stores each of said cell names with an OPC correction patterns for a related environmental profile; 
a replacement layout data creation unit configured to create replacement layout data by reading a replacement cell name corresponding to said environmental profile by referencing said cell replacement table; and 
an OPC correction pattern creation unit configured to import an OPC correction pattern corresponding to a replacement cell name from said cell library based on said replacement layout data.
